    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建设属于你自己的城市：</h2>《Global City》的画面极其出众，这里的住宅街区、巨型购物中心和高耸入云的建筑物一定会让你叹为观止。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731270/extras/f67d4be9fa076447ad5c4b74d8e886dd.poster.avif?t=1748530109\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731270/extras/f67d4be9fa076447ad5c4b74d8e886dd.webm?t=1748530109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731270/extras/f67d4be9fa076447ad5c4b74d8e886dd.mp4?t=1748530109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >采集资源：</h2>建设城市所需要的一切就在你的脚下。<br>好吧，准确地说，应该是埋在地下！采集天然资源和原材料，用它们来制作建筑物资、准备木材、制造塑料。凡是你的城市需要用到的资源，基本上都可以通过采集和自行制作得到。<br>别忘了，你还可以在《Global City》里从事贸易活动哦！努力迈上建设与贸易的新高峰吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731270/extras/dbfce736cded6be062f076ae3b1267ee.poster.avif?t=1748530109\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731270/extras/dbfce736cded6be062f076ae3b1267ee.webm?t=1748530109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731270/extras/dbfce736cded6be062f076ae3b1267ee.mp4?t=1748530109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >完成任务，收取税金，让人口不断增长：</h2>完成充满趣味性的任务，获取丰厚的奖励，让你能够更加顺利地推进主线故事。游戏中的税收系统还可以进一步增加你的收入。玩法很简单：你的城市里人口数量越高，你能收到的税金就越多！只要不断增加预算，你的城市就会发展得越来越好，你能建设的新项目也会变得越来越丰富。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731270/extras/4ff06f9b8dbc55d253286d05aefa1df9.poster.avif?t=1748530109\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731270/extras/4ff06f9b8dbc55d253286d05aefa1df9.webm?t=1748530109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731270/extras/4ff06f9b8dbc55d253286d05aefa1df9.mp4?t=1748530109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与好友们聊天：</h2>城市建设游戏，就是要跟好友们一起玩才更有意思。而在这款游戏中，你会惊喜地发现自己可以跟好友们一起聊天、交换资源、互相帮助，甚至还能联手参加比赛，赢取丰厚奖品，让游戏的乐趣大大提升！<br><br>● 随着城市的慢慢发展，有各种好玩的任务供你完成<br>● 建造炫酷的建筑和丰富多样的地点<br>● 赚取成就与奖励<br>● 从农业到太空飞行，各种科技任你开发<br>● 随心所欲地建设你自己理想中的城市！",
